com.nokia.maps.routing.enums

Interface TrafficMode


  • public interface TrafficMode
    This interface defines a series traffic mode constants for use with route calculation.

    • Field Summary

      Fields 
      Modifier and Type Field and Description
      static int DEFAULT
      This constant indicates traffic mode is default.
      static int DISABLED
      This constant indicates traffic mode is disabled.
      static int ENABLED
      This constant indicates traffic mode is enabled.

    • Field Detail

      • ENABLED

        static final int ENABLED
        This constant indicates traffic mode is enabled. Depending on the credentials of the requestor (Basic/Advanced API), the enabled option automatically selects appropriate constraints to take the actual traffic conditions into account (real time, patterns, predictive).
        See Also:
        Constant Field Values

      • DISABLED

        static final int DISABLED
        This constant indicates traffic mode is disabled. For requestors with Basic API credentials, only the NAVTEQ Speed Category and road closures are applied, for Advanced API requestors, additional (wherever available) free-flow information is applied.
        See Also:
        Constant Field Values

      • DEFAULT

        static final int DEFAULT
        This constant indicates traffic mode is default. The default mode considers all traffic information that are applicable for the selected TransportMode and the user is authorized to use.
        See Also:
        Constant Field Values
